<style>
    body {
        font-family: "Lato", sans-serif
    }

    .mySlides {
        display: none
    }
</style>
<body>
    <!-- Page content -->
    <div class="w3-content" style="max-width:2000px;margin-top:46px">

        <style>
            h1 {
                text-align: center;
            }
        </style>
        <h1>Welcome</h1>
        <!-- Automatic Slideshow Images -->
        <div class="mySlides w3-display-container w3-center">
            <img alt="Iceberg" src="/img/Images/Iceberg_with_hole_edit sized.jpg" style="width:100%" />
            <div class="w3-display-bottommiddle w3-container w3-text-white w3-padding-32 w3-hide-small">
                <h3><mark>Get Involved</mark></h3>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mySlides w3-display-container w3-center">
            <img alt="Dry lands" src="/img/Images/iceberg-greenland-nature-landscape-climate-change-global-warming-concept-iceberg-greenland-global-warming-concept-158020976 sized.jpg" style="width:100%" />
            <div class="w3-display-bottommiddle w3-container w3-text-white w3-padding-32 w3-hide-small">
                <h3><mark>Take It Step By Step</mark></h3>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mySlides w3-display-container w3-center">
            <img alt="Protests" src="/img/Images/istockphoto-1180544142-640x640 sized.jpg" style="width:100%" />
            <div class="w3-display-bottommiddle w3-container w3-text-white w3-padding-32 w3-hide-small">
                <h3><mark>Join The Community</mark></h3>
            </div>
        </div>
        <style>
            mark {
                background-color: black;
                color: white;
            }
        </style>
        <!-- The About Section -->
        <div class="w3-container w3-content w3-center w3-padding-64" style="max-width:800px" id="band">
            <h2 class="w3-wide">About Us</h2>
            <p class="w3-opacity"><i>We're committed to the cause</i></p>
            <p class="w3-justify">
                We're a non-profit organisation based in Auckland, New Zealand that was established in 2015
                In that time, we've expanded our network to over 150 global companies operating in 110 markets around the world. <br />Human activities such as burning fossil fuels like coal, oil, and gas, cutting down trees, and intensifying animal agriculture are all known to be contributing factors. According to new studies, the vast majority of fossil fuels must remain in the field. We can no longer afford to keep looking for new sources of oil, gas, and coal. <br /> Our climate is rapidly changing, posing a threat to the humans, animals, and places we cherish. Melting glaciers, rising seas, and new and more intense severe weather events are all expected in New Zealand. This will have far-reaching consequences for our lives and livelihoods, as well as for the animals, plants, and habitats that make us who we are. <br />Fortunately, we also know how to solve the problem: turn to 100% renewable energy. Renewable energy alternatives are expanding quickly and becoming more competitive than ever before, helping to protect the things we care about from the most severe climate threats while also enhancing human health, strengthening economies, and creating employment. <br /><br />So join us in the cause now and get involve! <br />
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Video Section -->
        <video width="1280" height="720" controls>
            <source src="~/vid/Videos/final_605866fedb305500916c1750_423460.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>

        <!-- The News Section -->
        <div class="w3-black" id="tour">
            <div class="w3-container w3-content w3-padding-64" style="max-width:800px">
                <h2 class="w3-wide w3-center">NEWS AND EVENTS</h2>
                <p class="w3-opacity w3-center"><i>Latest Updates</i></p><br>

                <ul class="w3-ul w3-border w3-white w3-text-grey">
                    <li class="w3-padding">September <span class="w3-tag w3-grey w3-margin-left">Climate Change Protest</span> <span class="w3-badge w3-right w3-margin-right">7</span></li>
                    <li class="w3-padding">October <span class="w3-tag w3-grey w3-margin-left">Sausage Sizzle</span> <span class="w3-badge w3-right w3-margin-right">28</span></li>
                    <li class="w3-padding">November <span class="w3-badge w3-right w3-margin-right">16</span> <span class="w3-tag w3-grey w3-margin-left">School Strike</span></li>
                </ul>

                <div class="w3-row-padding w3-padding-32" style="margin:0 -16px">
                    <div class="w3-third w3-margin-bottom">
                        <div class="w3-container w3-white">
                            <p><b>Welcome to Global Climate Vision</b></p>
                            <p class="w3-opacity">Published Thu 18 Feb 2021</p>
                            <p>New? We welcome you to our website and are delighted to show you around and give you a tour. This is our main platform into showing awareness of the cause so learn from here.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w3-third w3-margin-bottom">
                        <div class="w3-container w3-white">
                            <p><b>Participate in The March</b></p>
                            <p class="w3-opacity">Published Published Mon 8 Mar 2021</p>
                            <p>
                                We give you updates and vital information of any protests taking place at the moment or scheduled to happen. If you're interested in bringing awareness then portesting is a good way for other people to find out more about this issue.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w3-third w3-margin-bottom">
                        <div class="w3-container w3-white">
                            <p><b>Sign The Petition</b></p>
                            <p class="w3-opacity">Published Sat 20 Mar 2021</p>
                            <p>There are ongoing petitions which you could sign for free. All it takes is your name and email for governments and potential supporters to join in this cause.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <!-- The Contact Section -->
        <div class="w3-container w3-content w3-padding-64" style="max-width:800px" id="contact">
            <h2 class="w3-wide w3-center">CONTACT</h2>
            <p class="w3-opacity w3-center"><i>Have a querie? Tune us in!</i></p>
            <div class="w3-row w3-padding-32">
                <div class="w3-col m6 w3-large w3-margin-bottom">
                    <i class="fa fa-map-marker" style="width:30px"></i> Auckland, NZ<br>
                    <i class="fa fa-phone" style="width:30px"></i> Phone: 0800 123 456<br>
                    <i class="fa fa-envelope" style="width:30px"> </i> Email: globalclimatevision@gmail.com<br>
                </div>
                <div class="w3-col m6">
                    <h1>@ViewBag.Message</h1>
                    <form method="post">
                        <div class="w3-row-padding" style="margin:0 -16px 8px -16px">
                            <div class="w3-half">
                                <label asp-for="@Model.Name"></label>
                                <input class="w3-input w3-border" type="text" asp-for="@Model.Name" placeholder="Name">
                                <span class="text-danger" asp-validation-for="@Model.Name"></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="w3-half">
                                <label asp-for="@Model.Email"></label>
                                <input class="w3-input w3-border" type="text" asp-for="@Model.Email" placeholder="Email">
                                <span class="text-danger" asp-validation-for="@Model.Email"></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label asp-for="@Model.Message"></label>
                            <input class="w3-input w3-border" type="text" asp-for="@Model.Message" placeholder="Message">
                            <span class="text-danger" asp-validation-for="@Model.Message"></span>
                        </div>
                        <button class="w3-button w3-black w3-section w3-right" type="submit">SEND</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- End Page Content -->
    </div>

    <!-- Image of logo -->
    <img img src="~/img/Images/logo.jpg" class="w3-image w3-greyscale-min" style="width:100%">
</body>

<!-- Footer -->
